ffective as\nGeneral Relativity in matching observations. Thus, we can conclude that even\nobjects like NGC1052-DF2 are not in contrast, and are not obstacles, to the\nstudy and the definition of a reliable alternative to General Relativity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 13 Jun 2022 16:15:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-09"}
