ed\n$\\rm H_2$ reservoir of galaxy pairs. In addition, new FAST observations also\nreveal an HI absorber ($N_{\\text{HI}}\\sim 4.7 \\times 10^{21} \\text{ cm}^{-2}$),\nwhich may suggest gas infalling and the triggering of AGN activity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 13 Jun 2022 17:27:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-02"}
