 of $3\\times 10^{16}$ cm for cells with\nradial magnetic fields.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 14 Jun 2022 09:35:59 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 22 Aug 2022 12:05:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-26"}
